Bus Driver thread and life cycle.

BusDriverStates - Enum in states
Enum implementing the typical bus driver states: PARKING_AT_THE_ARRIVAL_TERMINAL - When the BusDriver is parked on the ArrivalQuay waiting for passengers DRIVING_FORWARD - Purely a transitional state, it represent when the bus driver is driving to the Departure Terminal PARKING_AT_THE_DEPARTURE_TERMINAL - When the BusDriver is parked on the DepartureQuay waiting for passengers to drop off DRIVING_BACKWARD - Represents the drive back to the ArrivalQuay
